			<p><b>USS Belleau Wood Operational Timeline</b></p><table border='0' cellspacing='0'><tr bgcolor='eeeeee'><td valign='top' align='right' nowrap><a href='/event/today/03/31/1943' alt='See all events on 31 Mar 1943' title='See all events on 31 Mar 1943' class='noStyle'>31 Mar 1943</a>&nbsp;</td><td>Belleau Wood was commissioned into service.</td></tr><tr bgcolor=''><td valign='top' align='right' nowrap><a href='/event/today/01/13/1947' alt='See all events on 13 Jan 1947' title='See all events on 13 Jan 1947' class='noStyle'>13 Jan 1947</a>&nbsp;</td><td>Belleau Wood was decommissioned from service.</td></tr></table><br /><p><b>Photographs</b></p><table cellpadding='2' cellspacing='0' border='0'><tr><td><a href='/photo.php?source=all&color=all&list=search&foreigntype=S&foreigntype_id=222'><img src="/images/imagemagick/tmb_ship_belleauwood2.jpg" border='0' alt='Belleau Wood in the Delaware River off the Philadelphia Navy Yard, Pennsylvania, United States, 18 Apr 1943, photo 1 of 2'></a></td><td><a href='/photo.php?source=all&color=all&list=search&foreigntype=S&foreigntype_id=222'><img src="/images/imagemagick/tmb_ship_belleauwood3.jpg" border='0' alt='Belleau Wood in the Delaware River off the Philadelphia Navy Yard, Pennsylvania, United States, 18 Apr 1943, photo 2 of 2; note location of SK, SC, and SG radar and YE aircraft homing beacon antennas'></a></td><td><a href='/photo.php?source=all&color=all&list=search&foreigntype=S&foreigntype_id=222'><img src="/images/imagemagick/tmb_ship_belleauwood5.jpg" border='0' alt='Belleau Wood entering Pearl Harbor, Hawaii, 22 Dec 1943'></a></td><td><a href='/photo.php?source=all&color=all&list=search&foreigntype=S&foreigntype_id=222'><img src="/images/imagemagick/tmb_ship_belleauwood4.jpg" border='0' alt='Belleau Wood underway in the Pacific Ocean about to enter Pearl Harbor, Hawaii, 22 Dec 1943'></a></td></tr></table><a href='/photo.php?source=all&color=all&list=search&foreigntype=S&foreigntype_id=222'>See all 18 photographs of